'''德里地铁'''（{{lang-hi|दिल्ली मेट्रो|Dillī Meṭro}}）是[[印度|印度]]首都[[新德里|新德里]]的[[城市轨道交通系统|城市轨道交通系统]]，并且该系统还服务首都圈内的卫星城——加兹阿巴德，法里达巴德，古尔冈，诺伊达，巴哈杜加尔和巴拉贝加尔。<ref>{{cite news| title = After 5 years of riding the New York City subway, I tried the Delhi Metro at the busiest time of the year - and it showed me exactly what I'm missing| accessdate = 24 February 2019| date = 24 November 2018| first = Tanya| last = Dua| work = Business Insider| url = https://www.businessinsider.in/after-5-years-of-riding-the-new-york-city-subway-i-tried-the-delhi-metro-at-the-busiest-time-of-the-year-and-it-showed-me-exactly-what-im-missing/articleshow/66778934.cms| archive-date = 2018-11-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181126092730/https://www.businessinsider.in/after-5-years-of-riding-the-new-york-city-subway-i-tried-the-delhi-metro-at-the-busiest-time-of-the-year-and-it-showed-me-exactly-what-im-missing/articleshow/66778934.cms| dead-url = yes}}</ref>德里地铁是印度迄今为止规模最大、最繁忙的城市轨道交通。同时德里也是继[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]之后，印度第二个开通地铁的城市。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://themetrorailguy.com/snapshot-of-how-indian-metro-systems-stack-up-with-one-another/|title=Snapshot of How India's Metro Systems Stack Up With One Another|access-date=2020-02-17|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201122031/https://themetrorailguy.com/snapshot-of-how-indian-metro-systems-stack-up-with-one-another/|dead-url=no}}</ref>德里地铁的敷设方式以高架为主，以地面和地下为辅。德里地铁使用两种轨距，分别是[[宽轨|印度宽轨]]和[[标准轨|标准轨]]。全线网每日运行2700多趟列车，运营时间为05:00至23:30。<ref name="Delhi-stations">{{cite news |author= |date=9 March 2019 |title=Delhi Metro's Ghaziabad, Noida extension sections thrown open to public |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/ghaziabad/delhi-metros-ghaziabad-noida-extension-sections-thrown-open-to-public/articleshow/68334111.cms |work=The Times of India |location=New Delhi |publisher=The Times of India |access-date=20 March 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127120043/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/ghaziabad/delhi-metros-ghaziabad-noida-extension-sections-thrown-open-to-public/articleshow/68334111.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NetLen"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.delhimetrorail.com/OtherDocuments/Firstimings.pdf|website=delhimetrorail.com|title=First and Last Train Timings|accessdate=16 June 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712165853/http://www.delhimetrorail.com/OtherDocuments/Firstimings.pdf|archivedate=12 July 2017}}</ref>

德里地铁始建于1998年，第一个高架区间为红线的Shahdara站至Tis Hazari站，于2002年投入运营；第一个地下区间为黄线的Vishwa Vidyalaya站至[[喀什米爾門站|喀什米爾門站]]，于2004年投入运营。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/it-all-started-15-xmas-days-ago/articleshow/62234532.cms|title=Delhi Metro: It all started 15 Xmas days ago|last=Roy|first=Sidharatha|date=25 December 2017|website=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|location=New Delhi|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180107021824/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/it-all-started-15-xmas-days-ago/articleshow/62234532.cms |archive-date=7 January 2018|url-status=live|access-date=16 January 2018}}</ref>线网的发展分为多个阶段，第一、第二、第三阶段分别已于2006年、2011年和2019年完成，第四阶段已于2019年12月30日正式动工。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.delhimetrorail.com/Project_Update.aspx|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-02-17|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201105707/http://www.delhimetrorail.com/Project_Update.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>德里地铁铁路有限公司（DMRC）由印度政府和德里政府共同出资组建，该公司负责德里地铁的建造和运营。<ref name="delhi300">{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/dmrc-to-join-global-club-of-metro-networks-having-span-of-over-300-km/articleshow/66417846.cms|title=Delhi Metro to join global club of metro networks having span of over 300 km | Delhi News - Times of India|website=The Times of India|accessdate=2020-02-17|archive-date=2018-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031162716/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/dmrc-to-join-global-club-of-metro-networks-having-span-of-over-300-km/articleshow/66417846.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="delhi300a">{{Cite web|url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/haryana/pm-inaugurates-kmp-expressway-ballabhgarh-mujesar-metro-rail-link/685668.html|title=PM inaugurates KMP expressway, Ballabhgarh-Mujesar Metro rail link|access-date=2020-02-17|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426200529/https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/haryana/pm-inaugurates-kmp-expressway-ballabhgarh-mujesar-metro-rail-link/685668.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

值得一提的是，[[古尔冈快捷都市铁路|古尔冈地铁]]和[[诺伊达地铁|诺伊达地铁]]是服务德里卫星城古尔冈和诺伊达的城市轨道交通系统，二者可与德里地铁相互换乘。[[古尔冈快捷都市铁路|古尔冈地铁]]和[[诺伊达地铁|诺伊达地铁]]的规模较小，各有一条线路，其中古尔冈地铁与德里地铁共享票务系统。DMRC于2019年2月5日接管了陷入财务困境的古尔冈地铁的运营业务，作为其自身网络的一部分。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/delhi-metro-decides-to-take-over-the-operations-of-gurgaon-rapid-metro-119020400037_1.html|title=Delhi Metro decides to take over the operations of Gurgaon Rapid Metro|last=Majumder|first=Arindam|date=4 February 2019|work=Business Standard India|access-date=4 February 2019|archive-date=2020-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405140824/https://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/delhi-metro-decides-to-take-over-the-operations-of-gurgaon-rapid-metro-119020400037_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

德里地铁曾是[[軌道運輸標竿聯盟|軌道運輸標竿聯盟]]（NOVA）的成員之一，現在則是[[国际地铁联盟|国际地铁联盟]]<ref>[http://www.nova-metros.org/  軌道運輸標竿聯盟（NOVA）] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nova-metros.org/ |date=20090803174527 }}{{en}}</ref>。

==历史==
[[File:Delhi_Metro_evolution.gif|right]]

德里地铁自1984开始计划，当时德里建设局和市艺术委员会提出建议要为城市开发一套综合的交通系统。印度政府和德里政府在1995年联合设立了[[德里地铁有限公司|德里地铁有限公司]]（DMRC）。1998年10月1日DMRC开始了地鐵第一期的建设工作。由於加爾各答地鐵早前曾因為政治原因、技術問題和政策延誤而超支12次和不斷推遲開通的日期，DMRC被賦予更大的自主度和權力以執行本項工程<ref name="expindia">{{cite news |url=http://www.expressindia.com/news/fullstory.php?newsid=84775 |title=Delhi Metro showcases public sector success |website=The Indian Express |date=13 April 2007 |accessdate=2009-09-10|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225005743/http://www.expressindia.com/news/fullstory.php?newsid=84775 |archivedate=2008-12-25 }}</ref>。DMRC曾向[[港鐵公司|香港地鐵公司]]諮詢地鐵的運營和建造方法<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtr.com.hk/eng/consultancy/clientlist.html |title=China Business/International Business |publisher=MTR |accessdate=2011-06-02|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110618223350/http://www.mtr.com.hk/eng/consultancy/clientlist.html |archivedate=2011-06-18}}</ref>。因此除了2000年印度鐵路部要求DMRC採用寬軌外<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2000/08/07/stories/140760l1.htm|title=Delhi Metro Rail to adopt BG system|last=|first=|date=2000-08-07|website=[[Business_Line|Business Line]]|publisher=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|publication-place=New Delhi|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201164121/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2000/08/07/stories/140760l1.htm|archive-date=2016-02-01|dead-url=no|accessdate=2018-01-16}}</ref>，地鐵的建設工程一直順利進行。2002年12月24日，時任印度總理[[阿塔爾·比哈里·瓦傑帕伊|阿塔爾·比哈里·瓦傑帕伊]]為[[德里地鐵紅線|德里地鐵紅線]]首通段主持啟用典禮。<ref name="first">{{Cite news |title=Indian PM launches Delhi metro |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/2602907.stm |newspaper=BBC News |date=2002-12-24 |accessdate=2010-04-22|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120422001958/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/2602907.stm |archivedate=2012-04-22}}</ref>

2004－2005年[[德里地鐵黃線|黃線]]一期逐步开通，[[德里地鐵藍線|藍線]]一期則於2005－2006年逐步開通，自此德里地鐵第一期工程於2006年11月11日全數完成，比原定時間提早三年，而且沒有超支<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2006/20061027/delhi.htm#1|title=The Tribune, Chandigarh, India – Delhi and neighbourhood|website=www.tribuneindia.com|access-date=2017-02-12|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312114559/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2006/20061027/delhi.htm#1|archivedate=2016-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2006/20060114/saturday/main1.htm|title=The Tribune – Magazine section – Saturday Extra|website=www.tribuneindia.com|access-date=2017-02-12|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070716153346/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2006/20060114/saturday/main1.htm|archivedate=2007-07-16}}</ref>。德里地鐵第二期工程全長124.6公里（77.4英里），共設85個車站，並已於2011年8月27日全數完成<ref name="Deadline">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-newdelhi/Delhi-Metro-confident-of-meeting-deadline/article14836060.ece|title=Delhi Metro confident of meeting deadline|author=Ramachandran|first=Smriti Kak|date=2007-09-17|newspaper=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|accessdate=2009-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303140135/http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-newdelhi/Delhi-Metro-confident-of-meeting-deadline/article14836060.ece|archive-date=2018-03-03|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>。第二期工程包括2009年开通的蓝线支线，以及2010－2011年逐步开通的[[德里地鐵綠線|綠線]]一期和[[德里地鐵紫線|紫線]]一期。

德里地鐵第三期工程共設26座地下車站、2條新線（粉紅線和洋紅線）和11條既有線的延伸<ref name="phase3">{{cite news|url=http://post.jagran.com/Delhi-Metro-rings-in-the-New-Year-under-new-chief-1325423311|title=Delhi Metro rings in the New Year under new chief|last=|first=|date=2012-01-01|newspaper=Jagran Post|accessdate=2018-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702223600/http://post.jagran.com/delhi-metro-rings-in-the-new-year-under-new-chief-1325423311|archive-date=2017-07-02|dead-url=no|publisher=[[Dainik_Jagran|Dainik Jagran]]|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>，新鐵路的總長度達167.27公里。此期工程已於2011年展開，曾有超過20部隧道鑽挖機同時進行工程。工程原訂於2016年全數完成，但因為土地取得問題，現時預計於2018年12月全數完成。2017年12月25日，總理[[納倫德拉·莫迪|納倫德拉·莫迪]]為印度首條無人駕駛的鐵路—德里地鐵洋紅線首通段主持啟用典禮<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/pm-modi-to-launch-delhi-metros-magenta-line-today-1791804|title=Delhi Metro Inauguration Live Updates: Botanical Garden-Kalkaji Mandir Section Thrown Open To Public|last=|first=|date= 2017-12-25|editor-last=Ray|editor-first=Amrita|website=[[NDTV|NDTV]]|publication-place=New Delhi|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230091708/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/pm-modi-to-launch-delhi-metros-magenta-line-today-1791804|archive-date=2017-12-30|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-01-16}}</ref>。

2020年12月28日，德里地鐵首個無人駕駛列車投入洋紅線運營<ref>{{cite news |title=PM Modi launches driverless train |url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/nation/current-affairs/281220/pm-modi-launches-driverless-train.html |accessdate=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112045228/https://www.deccanchronicle.com/nation/current-affairs/281220/pm-modi-launches-driverless-train.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

