===安全===
2002 - 2007年，德里警方負責德里地鐵的安全事務。自2007年起，德里地鐵的安全事務改由[[中央工業安全部隊|中央工業安全部隊]]負責。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-03-07/india/27875703_1_cisf-delhi-metro-baggage |title=CISF to take over Delhi Metro security |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2007-03-07|accessdate=2010-04-15|archive-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601151847/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-03-07/india/27875703_1_cisf-delhi-metro-baggage |dead-url=no }}</ref>地鐵系統主要依靠超過7000名安全部隊成員、金屬探測器、X射線行李檢查器和檢測犬維持治安。德里地鐵的車站、列車均設有[[閉路電視|閉路電視]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_delhi-metro-parking-areas-to-be-bought-under-cctv-cameras_1361509 |title=Delhi metro parking areas to be bought under CCTV cameras |newspaper=Daily News and Analysis |date=2010-03-21|accessdate=2010-04-15|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100826091055/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_delhi-metro-parking-areas-to-be-bought-under-cctv-cameras_1361509 |archivedate=2010-08-26}}</ref>，全地鐵系統共設有約5200個閉路電視，每個地下車站設有約45-50個鏡頭，每個高架車站設有約16-20個鏡頭。德里地鐵有限公司（DMRC）和中央工業安全部隊均會負責監控鏡頭<ref>{{Cite news |author=Megha Suri Singh |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-30/delhi/28140741_1_metro-stations-delhi-metro-metro-security |title=Moscow blasts put Metro security in alert mode |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2010-03-30|accessdate=2010-04-15|archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103182411/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-30/delhi/28140741_1_metro-stations-delhi-metro-metro-security |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德里地鐵亦會定期在車站和列車上舉行[[消防演習|消防演習]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-26/delhi/28141931_1_drills-metro-stations-disaster-preparedness |title=Mock drills at 4 Metro stations |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2010-03-26|accessdate=2010-04-15|archive-date=2013-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604025831/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-26/delhi/28141931_1_drills-metro-stations-disaster-preparedness |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

