==列車車輛==
[[File:Delhi_metro_six_coach_train_panoramic_view.jpg|thumb]]
德里地鐵並沒有統一各線的軌距，其中於德里地鐵第一期開通的線路（紅、黃、藍線）為寬軌（1676毫米），第二期及以後開通的線路則使用[[標準軌|標準軌]]（1435毫米）<ref name="StandardGauge">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/todays-paper/tp-logistics/article1044622.ece|title=Delhi Metro gets standard gauge train|last=|first=|date=2009-03-18|newspaper=[[Business_Line|Business Line]]|accessdate=2018-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811092034/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/todays-paper/tp-logistics/article1044622.ece|archive-date=2011-08-11|dead-url=no|publisher=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>。

地鐵第一期所使用的寬軌列車由[[現代Rotem|現代Rotem]]、[[三菱商事|三菱商事]]和[[三菱電機|三菱電機]]聯合製造。這批列車初期由[[現代Rotem|現代Rotem]]於南韓製造，後來則改由BEML透過技術轉移於[[邦加羅爾|邦加羅爾]]製造<ref>{{cite news |author=P. Manoj |url=http://www.hindu.com/2005/08/25/stories/2005082504340500.htm |title=BEML to rake in big money from proposed metro projects |newspaper=The Hindu |date=25 August 2005 |accessdate=2009-09-26|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328010423/http://www.hindu.com/2005/08/25/stories/2005082504340500.htm |archivedate=2008-03-28}}</ref>。這些列車外觀與[[港鐵市區綫韓製列車|港鐵的韓製列車]]相似，以4卡為一列，車廂闊3.2米，乘客可以透過車廂間之通道前往不同車廂。每列4卡列車可載客1500人<ref name="TOIcoaches">{{Cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2002-10-15/delhi/27293350_1_train-sets-first-metro-shahdara-tis-hazari |title=Second Metro rail arrives in Delhi |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2002-10-15 |accessdate=2009-09-26 |archive-date=2011-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110709210548/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2002-10-15/delhi/27293350_1_train-sets-first-metro-shahdara-tis-hazari |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而每卡車廂則設有50個座位和330個站位<ref name="DMRC stock">{{cite web |url=http://www.delhimetrorail.com/OtherDocuments/metro_museum/images/7.jpg |title=Rolling Stock: Ensuring Passenger Comfort, Safety and Reliability |publisher=[[Delhi_Metro_Rail_Corporation|DMRC]] |format=jpg |accessdate=2010-09-27|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101021052831/http://delhimetrorail.com/OtherDocuments/metro_museum/images/7.jpg |archivedate=2010-10-21 }}</ref>。所有列車車廂均設有空調、自動車門以及由[[微處理器|微處理器]]控制的煞車系統<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/2002/07/27/stories/2002072703730400.htm |title=Metro Rail gets first train |newspaper=The Hindu |date=2002-07-27|accessdate=2009-09-26|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708082826/http://www.hinduonnet.com/2002/07/27/stories/2002072703730400.htm |archivedate=2011-07-08 }}</ref>。這些4卡列車可於1.1公里的距離維持平均速度32公里每小時<ref name="DMRC stock"/>，並擴展成8卡，而車站月台在設計時亦已預留空間以便列車增至8卡行走<ref name="TOIcoaches"/>。

地鐵第二期所需要的寬軌列車則由[[龐巴迪運輸|龐巴迪運輸]]所製造，當時[[龐巴迪運輸|龐巴迪運輸]]接下的列車訂單總值高達1.1億美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bombardier.com/en/transportation/media-centre/press-releases/details?docID=0901260d8019ab49 |title=Bombardier to Deliver Further 76 MOVIA Metro Cars to Delhi Metro from Savli India Site |work=Press Release |publisher=Bombardier |date=2011-09-05|accessdate=2011-11-03|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111116062057/http://www.bombardier.com/en/transportation/media-centre/press-releases/details?docID=0901260d8019ab49 |archivedate=2011-11-16 }}</ref>。這批列車部分為4卡編組、部分為6卡編組。每列4卡列車可載客1178人，每列6卡列車則可載1792人。此批列車配備多項更完善的設施，包括監控鏡頭、行動裝置充電點、暖氣設備和經改良的空調系統<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-09-17/delhi/28098189_1_train-sets-present-trains-anand-vihar |title=Metro to get swankier, bigger coaches |newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] |date=2009-09-17 |accessdate=2009-09-26 |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105163832/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-09-17/delhi/28098189_1_train-sets-present-trains-anand-vihar |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

德里地鐵的標準軌列車主要由BEML於[[邦加羅爾|邦加羅爾]]製造，列車為4節編組。每列列車可載客1506人，<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/beml-delivers-indias-1st-standard-gauge-metro-car/articleshow/4999078.cms|title=BEML delivers India's 1st standard gauge metro car|last=|first=|date=11 September 2009|newspaper=[[The_Economic_Times|The Economic Times]]|accessdate=2018-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180115185943/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/beml-delivers-indias-1st-standard-gauge-metro-car/articleshow/4999078.cms|archive-date=2018-01-15|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>並可於1.1公里的距離維持平均速度達34公里每小時<ref name="DMRC stock"/>。每節車廂有50個座位、292個站位。這批列車配備監控鏡頭（車廂內外均設有）、行動裝置充電點、更完善的濕度控制系統以及由[[微處理器|微處理器]]控制的煞車系統<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/Trial-run-begins-on-first-standard-gauge-Metro-line/article16565587.ece|title=Trial run begins on first standard gauge Metro line|author=Ramachandran|first=Smriti Kak|date=2009-07-30|newspaper=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|accessdate=2018-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303140135/http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/Trial-run-begins-on-first-standard-gauge-Metro-line/article16565587.ece|archive-date=2018-03-03|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>。

在第三期的規劃中，德里地鐵曾考慮為部分新增線路引入[[磁懸浮列車|磁懸浮列車]]，但DMRC於2012年8月最終決定全數採用普通輪軌列車<ref>{{cite news|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/delhi-metro-says-no-to-maglev-technology/985544|title=Delhi Metro says no to Maglev technology|last=|first=|date=2012-08-08|newspaper=[[The_Indian_Express|The Indian Express]]|accessdate=2018-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201164122/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/delhi-metro-says-no-to-maglev-technology/985544|archive-date=2016-02-01|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>。
