==環境保護==
德里地鐵曾因為其保護環境的措施而獲得[[聯合國|聯合國]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Delhi-Metro-gets-UN-certificate-for-preventing-carbon-emission/articleshow/4169221.cms?referral=PM|title=Delhi Metro gets UN certificate for preventing carbon emission|last=|first=|date=2009-02-22|newspaper=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|accessdate=2018-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517111354/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Delhi-Metro-gets-UN-certificate-for-preventing-carbon-emission/articleshow/4169221.cms?referral=PM|archive-date=2014-05-17|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>、[[國際標準化組織|國際標準化組織]]<ref name="Ecofriendly">{{cite web |url=http://www.delhimetrorail.com/corporates/ecofriendly/ohsas18001.html |title=Delhi Metro gets OHSAS 18001 |publisher=[[Delhi_Metro_Rail_Corporation|DMRC]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607074341/http://www.delhimetrorail.com/corporates/ecofriendly/ohsas18001.html |archivedate=2008-06-07|accessdate=2009-09-10}}</ref>等國際組織所頒發的獎項。德里地鐵亦是世界上繼[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]]後第二座獲得ISO 14001環境管理認證的地鐵系統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usaid.gov/in/newsroom/press_releases/dec24_2.htm |title=Press Release: Delhi Metro Receives ISO 14001 For Eco-friendly Systems |publisher=[[USAID|USAID]] |date=2002-12-24 |accessdate=2010-09-27|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090913034728/http://www.usaid.gov/in/newsroom/press_releases/dec24_2.htm |archivedate=2009-09-13}}</ref>。大多數位於[[德里地鐵藍線|藍線]]的地鐵車站都會收集雨水以作環境保護。此外，德里地鐵亦參與了聯合國的[[清潔發展機制|清潔發展機制]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/delhi-metro-is-first-rail-project-to-earn-carbon-credits/articleshow/2676012.cms|title=Delhi Metro is first rail project to earn carbon credits|last=|first=|date=2008-01-05|newspaper=[[The_Economic_Times|The Economic Times]]|accessdate=2018-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180122181652/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/railways/delhi-metro-is-first-rail-project-to-earn-carbon-credits/articleshow/2676012.cms|archive-date=2018-01-22|dead-url=no|publication-place=New Delhi}}</ref>，透過在列車使用[[再生制動|再生制動]]系統節約能源，於[[排污交易|排污交易]]中獲得了400,000碳信用，成為世上首個獲得碳信用的鐵路項目<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/delhi/delhi-metro-on-track-to-earn-carbon-credits/|title=Delhi Metro on track to earn carbon credits|author=Sinha|first=Neha|date=2009-12-20|newspaper=[[The_Indian_Express|The Indian Express]]|accessdate=2018-01-22|deadurl=no|publication-place=New Delhi|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123072420/http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/delhi/delhi-metro-on-track-to-earn-carbon-credits/|archivedate=2018-01-23}}</ref>。

